textAfterTable: 08:00 PM by Offical Forums 0 News Rum Cellar DLC Launch Apr 30, 2015 - 11:16 AM - by Dolby The first campaign of Daybreak Games' new DLC strategy for EverQuest II has launched. The price of this campaign is $14.99. This campaign has come with many updates, additions and fixes. Here is a list of some of the features: 2 Solo Zones (1 Solo and 1 Advanced Solo) 3 Heroic Zones (1 Heroic, 1 Event Heroic, 1 Event Heroic-Challenge) Raid Zone with 10 Bosses Lots of Loot, including drops of a Rare Elite Mercenary and a Zeppelin Mount New Achievements and Titles New Adornments and a new adornment set bonus tier 30 New Collections Merchant who accepts Far Sea Ferrin (who also sells a Zeppelin Mount!)
